snippet.title: Lord Jamar Speaks on Amber Rose's "Finger in the Booty" Tweet to Kanye
snippet.description:
Since Amber Rose stirred a social media frenzy when she tweeted Kanye West "Finger in the booty a** b****,"  it sparked many jokes, memes, and conversations with people among the Hip Hop industry. The very outspoken Brand Nubian rapper, Lord Jamar doesn't think there is a gray line when it comes to a man being penetrated, and believes that once a man is penetrated, he is gay.

"That's like kindergarten for gay n*****. I don't think nothing should go in the a**, that should be exit only." He went on to say, "Once you're penetrated, you've given up your manhood."
